data.description: Lovely Ranch in West Akron! You will enjoy viewing this home. It has three bedroom and two full baths. There are hardwood floors in the majority of the home. The living room is spacious with a large picture window. The eat-in kitchen has been updated with plenty of cupboard space, recess lighting and tile back splash. All the appliances will stay. The full bath has been updated in January of 2024. The second bath off of the kitchen has a walk-in shower. There is a small dining room off of the kitchen as well. The basement has a large, finished area which gives extra space for whatever your needs may be. There is a one car attached garage. The outside fenced yard is perfect for cookouts or a pet area. Roof 2020, Furnace 2023, AC 2021.
